          "Logan Boese"
        ],
        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "Jason/Jasmine Walker - Ventrue Thinblood out of Denver, Colorado. Very much “Nothing from Nowhere.” They had an unexciting life and were embraced on little more than a whim to be an extra voice and extra pair of  hands to their sire. Their life was unremarkable and exceedingly average, and their death was unfortunately more of the same. They were mourned by their family and friends and then moved on from in the space of time it took their sire to teach them the basics of life and existence in the Camarilla and release them back to their own recognizance. While this might not do much for their self esteem, it did leave them with an unprecedented amount of freedom to go anywhere and do anything. As such, they’ve followed the want of their parent clan amd drifted on the winds to Los Angeles. Hearing many stories of the virtual utopia and it’s acceptance, they can only wonder if this is to be their New Home, or just the next in a line of stops."
        ],
        [
